Text.Value: How do I reach the Orphic Hammer?
Did Raphael prefer to be on top or beneath you?
Leave.
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*

EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW ANSWER - DELETE IF NOT NEEDED

Text.Value: Raphael... loves... only... Raphael.
How do I get my contract?
Does Raphael have any weaknesses in battle?
Did you ever turn into forms besides Raphael's?
Below... never on top... never.
Where does Raphael keep his secrets?
How did you end up here?
Safe... Secrets...
Haarlep... Incubus... sworn to Raphael.
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Who are you?
Sent by Mephistopheles... distract naughty son.
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Hidden behind... his... vanity.
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: SwD with Haarlep (incubus in House of Hope)
